From: The Libreswan Team <team@libreswan.org>
Date: Mon, 18 Jan 2021 23:29:05 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] IKEv2: Support for IKEv2 Labeled IPsec

This implements draft-ietf-ipsecme-labeled-ipsec-04
https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-ipsecme-labeled-ipsec-04

Based on initial patch by Kavinda Wewegama <kavinda.wewegama@forcepoint.com>
Resolves: https://github.com/libreswan/libreswan/pull/382

Co-authored-by: Sahana Prasad <sahana@redhat.com>
Co-authored-by: D. Hugh Redelmeier <hugh@mimosa.com>
Co-authored-by: Paul Wouters <pwouters@redhat.com>
